Reviews.Title: Quick shipping
Reviews.Author: D. Dunn
Reviews.Content: They were shipped quickly and they are exactly what they are advertised as.Not much to say about a barrel connector.  If it works and isn't damaged upon arrival it gets 5 stars.

Reviews.Title: BNC Female to Female Extenders
Reviews.Author: N. Padilla
Reviews.Content: I am a IT Professional and Consultant.  I just started offering Video Surveillance to my customer audience and thought that this would be a must for your tool inventory.  The last thing you need is to be scrambling for adapters and extenders.  These adapters are well made and durable.  And they just work.

Reviews.Title: Excellent adapter - excellent price
Reviews.Author: Ernie Gubbels "EJG Omaha"
Reviews.Content: This coupler is exactly what you would expect. The overall construction is good and fits standard BNC connectors quite well.
